{"tid":1770812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【呼籲】請向前看，原諒美心！","createTime":"2019-12-05T11:49:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T10:20:11.000Z","uid":202464,"like":2,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"be5e9265d9ef4fde6889a943f67c34158e385ab3","tid":1770812,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T11:49:45.000Z","msg":"1. 美心太子女伍淑清年紀老邁，可能腦筋不清。佢過去所講既奶共言論千祈唔好當係真。<br />\n<br />\n2. 美心西餅唔肯寫「光復香港」、「時代革命」字句，只係保護黃絲顧客。因為工場廚房佬都係低學歷藍絲/大陸人。你要佢地寫反中亂港賀詞，佢地分分鐘係蛋糕上面加「精」報復。<br />\n<br />\n3. 大家為難美心，只會令背後英資怡和難做。英國佬鬼計多端，洋行大班會去英國上議院打小報告，阻攔BNO平權。<br />\n<br />\n4. 千錯萬錯，都係美心太子女伍淑清既錯。玻璃、招牌、蛋糕&hellip;&hellip;都是無辜。為地球先生著想，減少浪費啦。<br />\n<br />\n5.  最後，伍氏家族大把錢，一間鋪一百幾十萬，佢地轉頭都賺得返。大家無謂做無謂野了。向前看，原諒美心啦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（儲滿一百負皮可以問返美心拎稿費。）"},{"pid":"e57475637bea7b7c72d848403179f5861ae2052a","tid":1770812,"uid":226886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T11:50:45.000Z","msg":"原諒你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"656eca79cf212a77e995a7348e380e9425159dd0","tid":1770812,"uid":143321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T11:51:18.000Z","msg":"伍氏家族大把錢<br />\n使咩我地原諒"},{"pid":"380c27e9ad51f0825fafc3b8b31e899993fd4569","tid":1770812,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e57475637bea7b7c72d848403179f5861ae2052a","tid":1770812,"uid":226886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T11:50:45.000Z","msg":"原諒你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T11:51:34.000Z","msg":"再糾纏美心，只會中計"},{"pid":"25b62743c255f45849fd357dc12dc27c49ae58a3","tid":1770812,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"656eca79cf212a77e995a7348e380e9425159dd0","tid":1770812,"uid":143321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T11:51:18.000Z","msg":"伍氏家族大把錢<br />\n使咩我地原諒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T11:52:26.000Z","msg":"你地唔夠佢鬥架。收手啦！"},{"pid":"e8d73bb18c6f0e2ed53adfe2869719578119b4ad","tid":1770812,"uid":120913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T11:53:03.000Z","msg":"［呼籲］請你收嗲，左膠死開！"},{"pid":"6cec024f1fb9bcd720de55f93a99e4f74735e6dc","tid":1770812,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8d73bb18c6f0e2ed53adfe2869719578119b4ad","tid":1770812,"uid":120913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T11:53:03.000Z","msg":"［呼籲］請你收嗲，左膠死開！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T11:56:22.000Z","msg":"大家都累了。"},{"pid":"0bf856559db31d2901a4fc59f81ff2ba87dbe28f","tid":1770812,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T11:59:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />愛美心"},{"pid":"b92093fdc105bb1b4bc9c0a16baccb43940aab78","tid":1770812,"uid":140326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T12:08:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9609f439e72d391b7a8ce66d221065a03a47510","tid":1770812,"uid":140326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T12:12:07.000Z","msg":"【正視聽】不要叫美心伍淑清，試著說世界之窗伍淑清<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1768370\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1768370</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a397c2d89ddf63100c1291a04723ab4e1e2ec48a","tid":1770812,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T12:17:08.000Z","msg":"美心最愛香港人！"},{"pid":